OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, There's nothing David Jason loves more 
OL,8, than the sea and its strange creatures,
OL,9, in particular theCgentle and almost    
OL,10,Cextinct manatee.GDavid explains:       
OL,12, "This large, lumbering creature is a   
OL,13,Cdistant relative of the elephantGand   
OL,14, unfortunately not known for its looks! 
OL,16, "Its population is at crisis point.    
OL,17, Fewer than 2,000 manatees remain and,  
OL,18, dying at a rate of 200 a year, they    
OL,19, could beCextinct within two years."    
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````1/5``
OL,21,C         by Bernadette Carroll         
OL,22,D]G MCHECK OUT THE GREEN SCENE p160     
