OL,1,R?/`pp0ppp`ujbs`pp0up`u W      pp  
OL,2,R/m|jk57"7jjj757"7 W  `,d.!"+4
OL,3,R|~j~5} 5jjj}55 5 W   )`q&)8%
OL,4,B``R*/B``````````R(,/%B``C   W  (ao=(! 
OL,5,CDAVID JASON                   Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, David Jason, who rose to fame in Only  
OL,8, Fools and Horses, says theCpopulation  
OL,9,Cexplosion in FloridaGis responsible for
OL,10, the decline of the manatee.            
OL,12, "Every single day,Cover one thousand   
OL,13,Cpeople move to Florida,"Ghe explains.  
OL,15, "They come here for the promise of a   
OL,16, lifestyle, a lifestyle that's killing  
OL,17, the manatee. You see everybody wants a 
OL,18,Cwaterfront home."GTo build these, the  
OL,19, manatees' natural habitat is destroyed.
OL,20,B``````````````````````````````````2/5``
OL,21,C  Green SceneG160      CEco SceneG148  
OL,22,D] GMPROTECT YOUR LOCAL WOODLAND p163   
