OL,1,R?/`pp0ppp`ujbs`pp0up`u W      pp  
OL,2,R/m|jk57"7jjj757"7 W  `,d.!"+4
OL,3,R|~j~5} 5jjj}55 5 W   )`q&)8%
OL,4,B``R*/B``````````R(,/%B``C   W  (ao=(! 
OL,5,CDAVID JASON                   Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, "For each manatee in Southern Florida, 
OL,8, there are overC400 pleasure boats,"    
OL,9, says David Jason, who stars in A Touch 
OL,10, of Frost.                              
OL,12, "The manatee likes to swim very slowly 
OL,13, just beneath the surface, exactly at   
OL,14,Cthe same depth as the boat's propeller.
OL,16, "Last year, over a hundred manatees    
OL,17, wereCkilled by boats and countless     
OL,18,Cothers maimed or injured.GThey're not  
OL,19, a pretty sight..."                     
