OL,5,CDAVID JASON                   Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7,C"Marine biologistsGare now working with
OL,8, manatees to test the extent of their   
OL,9, hearing and in particular the different
OL,10, frequencies of speed boats," says a    
OL,11, concerned David Jason.                 
OL,13,G"Only the next couple of years will    
OL,14,Gtell whether or not this research will 
OL,15,GcomeCin time to save the manatee.G     
OL,17, "In the end it may turn out to be      
OL,18,Cfutile,Gas a mystery disease is now    
OL,19, ravaging the remaining population."    
