OL,5,CDAVID JASON                   Wx}}b4  
OL,6,                             W`~    
OL,7, "It's very hard to believe that the    
OL,8, manatee will eventuallyCgo the same way
OL,9,Cas the dodo,"Gsighs David Jason.       
OL,11, "Another victim of man's desire to     
OL,12, dominate the landscape -Cjust another  
OL,13,Cpicture in a history book..."          
OL,15,BGFor more of David's discoveries and  
OL,16, thoughts on the manatee and other      
OL,17, marine creatures, watchCDavid Jason In 
OL,18,CHis Element, Feb 17, 8.30pm on ITV.    
